# Small Proofs from Congruence Closure

This file is a transition-time build anchor for the public page.
The canonical publication record and assets live in
`pubs/2022-fmcad-smallproofs/`.

Edit `pubs/2022-fmcad-smallproofs/publication.json` for structured publication
data, keep the abstract/BibTeX/assets in the same directory, and use
`pubs/2022-fmcad-smallproofs/extra.dj` for any rare page-specific extra
content.
